summary:
Creative, passionate and dedicated professional with broad expertise in handling visual projects, illustrative creation and visual conceptualisation. Mix of positive thinking, problem solving, easy communication and technical skills proven by 10+ years of professional experience. Able to identify opportunities and build mutual relationships with clients, making visual impact in expressing stories hidden in fine details.
